01:00:37,467 --> 01:00:38,468
It wasn't a dream.

821
01:00:40,053 --> 01:00:40,887
This kid...

822
01:00:42,430 --> 01:00:43,431
existed in real life.

823
01:01:15,672 --> 01:01:17,256
I was beaten up whenever it rained.

824
01:01:18,591 --> 01:01:19,592
So

825
01:01:20,927 --> 01:01:23,096
I never went out after it rained.

826
01:01:23,346 --> 01:01:25,932
That's why I have never seen
a rainbow before.

827
01:01:27,100 --> 01:01:30,061
The girl who showed me a rainbow
for the first time.

828
01:01:36,234 --> 01:01:38,111
I wanted to be a grown-up for her.

829
01:01:40,238 --> 01:01:41,656
I didn't want to die.

830
01:01:42,699 --> 01:01:44,200
I'm Yeon-seo.

831
01:01:44,325 --> 01:01:45,243
Lee Yeon-seo.

832
01:01:45,660 --> 01:01:46,577
What about you?

833
01:01:47,495 --> 01:01:48,329
I'm...

834
01:01:48,996 --> 01:01:49,914
I'm...

835
01:01:50,832 --> 01:01:51,958
My name is...

836
01:02:13,688 --> 01:02:14,772
My name is

837
01:02:15,440 --> 01:02:16,315
Seong-u.

838
01:02:16,399 --> 01:02:17,275
Seong-u.

839
01:02:17,358 --> 01:02:18,192
Yoo Seong-u.

840
01:02:18,651 --> 01:02:19,610
Yoo Seong-u.

841
01:02:51,184 --> 01:02:54,228
Why did you let me remember everything?

842
01:02:54,312 --> 01:02:55,813
I'm so sorry.

843
01:02:56,856 --> 01:02:58,024
It won't take long.

844
01:02:58,107 --> 01:02:59,025
I promise.

845
01:02:59,108 --> 01:03:01,652
If a guy tells you to wait for him
and that he needs some time...

846
01:03:01,736 --> 01:03:02,820
Is he married?

847
01:03:02,904 --> 01:03:04,530
Stop crying because of that jerk.

848
01:03:04,614 --> 01:03:06,741
He's unbelievable.
He pretended to be so noble.

849
01:03:06,824 --> 01:03:08,826
Don't mind him
and don't even listen to him.

850
01:03:08,910 --> 01:03:11,329
I will make her love and be happy,
so get lost.

851
01:03:11,496 --> 01:03:12,789
I wanted to become a grown-up.

852
01:03:12,872 --> 01:03:14,665
And as a strong and powerful grown-up,

853
01:03:14,749 --> 01:03:16,125
I wanted to protect her.

854
01:03:16,292 --> 01:03:18,753
What are you talking about?
Why would he die?

855
01:03:19,086 --> 01:03:21,130
Are you well, Dan?

